shows.title: Wallace & Gromit: Vengeance Most Fowl
shows.plot_overview: Gromit’s concern that Wallace is becoming too dependent on his inventions proves justified, when Wallace invents a “smart” gnome that seems to develop a mind of its own. When it emerges that a vengeful figure from the past might be masterminding things, it falls to Gromit to battle sinister forces and save his master… or Wallace may never be able to invent again!

shows.title: Civil War
shows.plot_overview: In the near future, a group of war journalists attempt to survive while reporting the truth as the United States stands on the brink of civil war.
